{"id": "94", "instruction": "What is the center and radius of circle? $$\\left\\{\\begin{aligned} {{{}}} & {{} {{} {{} x^{2}+y^{2}+z^{2}=4}}} \\\\ {{{}}} & {{} {{{} x^{2}+y^{2}+z^{2}+x+y+z-7=0}}} \\\\ \\end{aligned} \\right.$$\n\nOptions:\nA. $$( 2, 1, 1 ), r=4$$\nB. $$( 2, 1, 2 ), r=5$$\nC. $$( 1, 1, 1 ), r=1$$\nD. $$( 1, 0, 1 ), r=2$$\nE. $$( 1, 1, 2 ), r=2$$\nF. $$( 0, 1, 1 ), r=1$$\nG. $$( 1, 1, 0 ), r=3$$\nH. $$( 0, 0, 1 ), r=4$$\nI. $$( 1, 2, 1 ), r=3$$\nJ. $$( 1, 0, 0 ), r=5$$", "output": "C"}
